cross: Oncidium Tiger Hambühren × Oncidium Jubilee Volunteer

measurements.description: Seventeen flowers on one staked, branching, 114-cm inflorescence; sepals and petals margins undulate, yellow, random faint cordovan spots, heavily blotched cordovan centrally; lip yellow, lighter yellow distally, mid lobe blotched cordovan, callus dark yellow; column light yellow, anther cap light cordovan; substance firm; texture matte.
